264 1052 978 (  The tables in Clause 24 of Iterator Requirements include) 978 SB
264 1102 1036 (  mutative operations such as ++ and =, but make no mention) 1036 SB
264 1152 1068 (  of constness.  We should distinguish which operations require) 1068 SB
264 1202 1038 (  a non-const operand and which can be performed on a const) 1038 SB
264 1252 846 (  operand.  \(e.g. is *a allowed on a const iterator?\)) 846 SB
264 1352 368 ( Proposed Resolution:) 368 SB
264 1402 982 (  All operations found in the tables can be applied to const) 982 SB
